{"tid":1999153,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"AKB48本家討論區#54 成個星期冇人理 本家係咪就冚旗!??","createTime":"2020-05-03T03:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T19:17:40.000Z","uid":231040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88171e014ea4549b1b057364277d6a17df7e5e28","tid":1999153,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/atctwn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13THIII.jpg?resize=1024%2C682&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fatctwn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F13THIII.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C682%26ssl%3D1&h=2a3c8cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/f80e2b05dc56f45ed67f2b6dbb688ecfcc3aa319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2Ff80e2b05dc56f45ed67f2b6dbb688ecfcc3aa319.jpg&h=3c1b4218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/34cc31f46e5c27e87e3f6fbc33cd0a69/tumblr_p8o1szN96E1t7i4f6o2_540.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F34cc31f46e5c27e87e3f6fbc33cd0a69%2Ftumblr_p8o1szN96E1t7i4f6o2_540.gifv&h=de9be904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總監督話要屌醒哂你班本家飯： <br />\n成個星期都唔開Post，仲要係俾個泡飯嚟開番，係咪當本家死咗嘞!?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然最近推得勁慢,但本區宗旨係悠閒既聚腳點,唔求一個月爆po,但求大家得閒貼下圖吹兩句就好,歡迎各路人馬加入本家大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙大家錯愛,本PO可以開到53,想再次重申開番本家PO既原意係希望俾各位本家飯有個集中地吹奏自己個推,無論貼圖又好、放mb活動既情報上黎又好、打機過唔到、番工辛苦吐苦水,甚至想講自己同MB已經有默契,心入面有各自既位置都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白到現今世代好多48飯都係各團互走,亦唔介意大家偶爾貼下其他分團既成員介紹俾其他會員知道,總之唔好貼到或宣傳到呢度變左100%既分團討論區就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢邊規矩好簡單:<br />\n1. 唔明或有野想知可以問其他巴打或google。<br />\n2. 討論過程實有爭論或嘈交,基本上唔好人身攻擊就得。<br />\n3. 明白到理論上唯有完美既奈奈外無一個MB係完美既,黑還黑、恥笑還恥笑,唔好太過分傷到成員既飯既感情就好了。<br />\n4. 8仔算唔算本家?有人算有人唔算,呢邊無咩所謂都歡迎討論同吹奏。<br />\n5. 本PO歡迎mb生日圖海洗1001,唔好分開2日洗就ok。<br />\n6. 萬一真係咁唔好彩有會員唔小心自爆左,麻煩大家唔好引用落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 如果係吹奏46團或想撩人過檔請麻煩番去46團既相關po,有緣既話巴打們自然會過去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8. 通常啲會員掛住某mb神id但吹奏既永遠都係第二個<br />\n9. 本家PO飯聚主要話題：喂,你飛撚夠未<br />\n10. 世界仔剩係反牙達<br />\n11. 本區識日文班人睇5ch攞料,唔識個班就睇百度/貓頭<br />\n12. 本家區三大黨派:小栗派&amp;柏木軍&amp;萌夏黨(已滅)<br />\n13. MARY:好想一生一世守護__ __BB豬(每星期更新)<br />\n14. 唔好諗咁多,本家全純血出既單曲應該唔會有機會出到<br />\n15. 矢作萌夏割禾青正仆街<br />\n16. NGT睇佢握手會仲有咁多人握就知佢唔會執<br />\n17. 已經消失的10專<br />\n18. 以為睇垃圾泡狗就好似高人一等咁,得喇得喇,知啦知啦,叻啦叻啦,行開啲啦,屌你老母<br />\n19. 世界大事：11月7日係完美既奈奈同轆轆既生日<br />\n20. 本家新希望:豬琪BB<br />\n21. 本家飯係時候要懺悔<br />\n<br />\n一切既知識:<br />\n<a href=\"http://google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjggexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=6393b182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://google.com</a><br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝會然I am Mary：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjggexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=3edb22d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n握手流程攻略 KEEP住UPDATE<br />\n<br />\n其他諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac4f6a3197c134418e5416